{"tid":1286884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家唔好比武漢事件騎劫反送中","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T04:06:43.000Z","uid":253252,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bdd00b5abc5d1157da545d9c757b059771fdf5e","tid":1286884,"uid":253252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"記住我地係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求</span></span>呀, 而家好似大家都少提左但呢五樣係我地運動既核心!!! <br />\n<br />\n唔好再對大陸人心存啲不切實際既幻想, 就算佢地知武漢發生咩事佢地都只會覺得佢地係反動份子, 個垃圾焚化場唔係起係佢地屋企隔離就得。比中共摧殘左咁多年, 大陸人思想上已經冇得救, 更加唔係由自身難保既香港人去救。77你會係九龍見到果啲大陸人落嚟shopping架咋, 唔係嚟了解國情架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更重要既係, 一旦我地公開咁將反送中同武漢事件混為一談, 外國就好難出聲支持我地。 因為武漢唔似香港有特別行政區地位 + 中英聯合聲明, 外國可以出師有名; 武漢就真係中國內政, 出坦克又點, 新疆做埋種族大清洗都未有人出聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港作為一個城市可以抵抗中共嘅最大籌碼我地既特殊國際地位, 唔好搞到自身失左優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話敵人嘅敵人就係朋友, 但武漢果啲唔係敵人嘅敵人, 果啲係敵人嘅僕人咋; 佢地理撚得你自由民主人權, 根本追求嘅就係唔同嘅野。你會同情佢地, 但佢唔會支持返我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係話完全唔理呢件事, 你地想嘅可以組下網上打手團去微博洗下版, 或者自己搵一group人去同啲大陸人講下呢件事, 如果煩到中共唔敢放人落香港都叫落得清淨。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但一定一定!!!唔好公開將呢件事同反送中扯上關係!!!</span> 林奠同政府啲走狗已經想模糊焦點架啦, 我地一定要keep住提先會可以繼續凝聚本土同國際嘅支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850eea62025b5e35ef3646cff6b543619ac15a4c","tid":1286884,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3b3f97527eb41b117122af639676ce6d692e1fa","tid":1286884,"uid":253252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42167db5e5b7e042bd8be7d0e9a7e737929aedda","tid":1286884,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"講得幾好"},{"pid":"e3bc0ec04c92968d2af4d2cc103a6ba5579787f0","tid":1286884,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n大家無衝突<br />\n團結則贏<br />\n分化則輸"}]}